description: “After the sage Dada Thakur spares James Jensen, they are attacked by the colonel Timothy Townsend. The Guru tells James what siddhis Sadhu is capable of doing and they escape by shrinking to subatomic size. Later the colonel blames Jensen for all of the problems that happened. James them wakes up in a house in the woods where group of natives are living. He is put through traning and learns how to be 'heavy as a rock' and 'light as the air' by using the force of Brahman.”

The one name that still speaks volumes of how absolute power can corrupt is Caligula. Assassination attempts against him have failed and now Caligula demands blood vengeance. Felix must keep his focus and sanity in the face of so much misery and horror.
